properties.name: Goddess and Grocer
properties.description: Posted by Swinka121646 North Damen Avenue, Chicago, ILNot in a mood to cook? Goddess and Grocer (2 locations in Chicago) will be happy to provide a wide variety of prepared meals to please most foodies out there. Plus they have wine, cheese, chocolates and, of course, Das Caramelini!

properties.name: Intelligentsia Coffee and Tea
properties.description: Posted by Swinka12 3123 North Broadway Street, Chicago, iLUn-Starbucks! This Chi-town own Coffee and Tea outfit roast their beans locally and specialize in fair trade coffee from all over the world. 3 Locations in Chicago. Das Caramelini can be found in each locaton and you can buy either individual or boxed caramels. http://www.intelligentsiacoffee.com/

properties.name: Moveable Feast
properties.description: Posted by Swinka12321 Franklin St, Geneva, ILhttp://www.moveablefeastgeneva.com/ Home of Oprah\'s favorite fugdey brownies (I tasted them too and they\'re to die for!)Kim and Matt Lennart have the most adorable space, gorgeous and tasty treats and, of course, Das Caramelini :)

properties.name: Paulina Meat Market
properties.description: Posted by Swinka123501 North Lincoln Ave, chicago, ILHomemade sausages? check! Proscuitto? Yes, sir! 100 different kinds of meat, cheese, and myriad other items? Oui! Paulina Meat Market has been here since 1949 and for a good reason: this family owned business really knows how to attract customers and keep them. http://www.paulinameatmarket.com/

properties.name: Sam's Wines and Spirits
properties.description: Posted by Swinka121919 Skokie Valley Rd.http://www.samswine.com/about_highland.php Sam\'s wine and Spirits has been a true Chicago wine destination for over 60 years!

properties.name: Southport Grocery and Cafe
properties.description: Posted by Swinka12 3552 N. Southport Chicago, IL 60657 http://www.southportgrocery.com/ If you want to sample delicious fare that Lisa and Jesse serve daily to the hip and happening crowd,best to come early as it\'s always crowded. Sample Das Caramelini on selected weekends

properties.name: the bottle shop
properties.description: Posted by Swinka12 1138 Central Avenuehttp://www.thebottleshop.net/ Amy and Joe\'s wine selections are outsanding and won\'t break the bank. We like to pair Red House Wine (0) that we find at Bottle shop with Chocolate and Toasted Walnut caramel
